        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1680",
        "content": "So Margaret rose up and began slowly to undress herself, feeling the full luxury of acting leisurely, late as it was, after all the past hurry of the day.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
