        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1680/142282/1680_142282_000014_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1680",
        "content": "Margaret rather encouraged this light, merry way of viewing her father's acquaintance with mr Thornton, because she felt that her mother was inclined to look upon this new friendship of her husband's with jealous eyes.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1680_142282_000014_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1680/142282/1680_142282_000014_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1680",
        "content": "As long as his time had been solely occupied with his books and his parishioners, as at Helstone, she had appeared to care little whether she saw much of him or not; but now that he looked eagerly forward to each renewal of his intercourse with mr Thornton, she seemed hurt and annoyed, as if he were slighting her companionship for the first time.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1680_142282_000015_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1680/142282/1680_142282_000015_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1680",
        "content": "The question always is, has everything been done to make the sufferings of these exceptions as small as possible?",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
