        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1680",
        "content": "The limits by which this rule of her aunt's had circumscribed Margaret's independence had been silently rebelled against at the time: and she had doubly enjoyed the free walks and rambles of her forest life, from the contrast which they presented.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
